  "technicalDetails": "<p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li>One GameState Component, the server side code. Players that are ready is replicated to all.</li><li>One PlayerController Component, so the player can send a request when it´s ready.</li><li>One GameInstance Subsystem, For easy access to the system both for clients and the server.</li><li>Four Delegates/Events that are called on both server and on all clients. OnAllPlayersReady, OnPlayerReady, OnTimeoutReached, OnServerStartWaiting.</li><li>The components will automatically be added if they do not exist. They can also be added directly in the editor.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Code Modules:</strong></p><ul><li> WaitForPlayers, Runtime</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 10</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 3</p><p>Network Replicated: Yes</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Windows, Mac, Linux, IOS, Android. (Only Windows tested, should work on other platforms)</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Windows, Mac, Linux, IOS, Android. (Only Windows tested, should work on other platforms)</p><p>Documentation: https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vT-jShq6rdrPH5iblWn_ue9ktoaOAW-9TF7Ojypa66wsNnTkDhR4nqzlv_6nKgKEry7iYl39m6_P3M-/pub</p><p><strong>Example Project</strong>: <em><u>Engine-&gt;Plugins-&gt;WaitForPlayers-&gt;ExampleLevel</u></em></p><p>Important/Additional Notes: This plugin is using unreal engine´s plugin ModularGameplay.</p><p>You can contact me here: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/azWURcymGY\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://discord.gg/azWURcymGY</a></p>",
